Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:10.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how we'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:24.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:26.55,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,As for the initiation of the mission—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:29.29,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you headed out, Kana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.56,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:36.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately going to spend her pay, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Not all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:42.05,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally able to send some back home so I thought it'd be nice to send a present along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:42.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And then after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,A little reward for yourself as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:46.29,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:50.87,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Because the first month was training, you didn't get paid for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:52.40,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,You must be happy! {saisho no ikkagetsu ha kenshuu de tadabatarake datta mon ne. ureshii deshou}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.40,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  But I was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:03:00.82,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I had heard that it's expected for wages to be late, and that it's normally provided in the form of military currency...{okyuuryou chihai ga atarimae tte kiitetashi futsuu ha gunpyou datte iu kara...} {TLC - military stock? The military has stock now? D: ~Sumi}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.88,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are!  Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd get real money, and on time too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.10,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that's why our platoon has—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:22.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!  That is—  Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:23.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a market set up in town today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:24.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen one before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:30.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Your first paycheck and your first day off.  There are all sorts of firsts for you today, aren't there, Kana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:33.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about work and go enjoy yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!  I'll be back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to make her suspicious! {suspect something's up}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:04:04.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But really, common sense tells you {if you just used your brain a little/common sense, it says, you'd realize that }it's impossible we'd be paid on time out here, in the middle of nowhere! {datte jyoushiki de kangaettara konna henkyou de chihai mo sezu ni okyuuryou wo dashite moraeru wake nai jyanai desu ka!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:13.48,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, Kanata believed it so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Her innocent gullibility {honesty }is one of her best qualities. {like...straightforwardness, a little bit of innocence/naivety thrown in that word too}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:22.69,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you guys, who were immediately suspicious of{distrusted/wondered} where the money came from. {not just wondered, but doubted/suspected}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:23.82,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:24.30,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:29.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:34.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0165,,Let's forget about our serious jobs too, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0165,,Well distilled{made}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.97,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be lowering the price any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!  I got a little too caught up—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.24,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like all the preparations are complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  All without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,There's a problem on my end though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,And I have a suggestion as to what you should do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.30,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Could you possibly explain yourself more clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:27.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:32.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,This one is cute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:53.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So you all are the ones selling these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Have you taken a liking to the goods then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They're not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:11.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But you see, there's just one little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.18,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  And what might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:18.56,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,To sell even just this many of them would take a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:22.73,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And when we think about it, it's a little too much work for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.69,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And so—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:26.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving discounts is part of our policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,The price itself is a part of its delicate flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No one's asking you to lower the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.95,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.62,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to shoot, go ahead and try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:52.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, before you manage that, this thing will blow a hole right through your head instead. {as opposed to his hat. his head will be substituted}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then—!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Not very intelligent, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.53,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,This is your punishment for looking poorly on us. {looking at us cheaply}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep well, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.78,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,{yo. that's mad scary. they shouldn't be able to do that. i'm reallyyy hoping they didn't actually hit those men right now.}{o_o they look like those old gangsters with those outfits:D}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.29,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:08.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the Big Boss' gifts?! {here it's oyabun. up there it was kashira.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's only worth something if we're still alive to give them to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:15.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me that there were such dangerous people here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:21.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never coming back to this town again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:27.98,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:28.98,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.24,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's all, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:38.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,{THANKGOODNESS ;_;}{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:37.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Man, my heart was pounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:40.74,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Renchuu,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we managed to fake them out, huh? {i use huh to much. if there's a huh at the end of a sentence, it's almost always a desu ne, deshou, etc. kind of phrase}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:43.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,We thank you for your cooperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:49.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.  No need for thanks.  With the central mafia{a location} out of the way, our business will go up as well.  {chuuou no mafia nanka norikonde koraretara shoubai agattari desu kara}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,You watch out for us and we'll watch out for you!  Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:58.76,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But of course... you'll be reimbursing us for our roles in this little play, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:02.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear!  Mikael-san, you're such a joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.40,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joking at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:10.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're now in the realm of business, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't remember her name ><}Should I take care of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:17.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Were you guys the ones who crushed those vagrants' car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:21.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:24.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like someone crushed their car pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:33.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,And inside there's a heap of war spoils they've hounded up and bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pretend as if I bought them and we'll split the profit equally.  How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:40.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.14,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.14,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:49.69,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Guess this farce is finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.15,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,But I was just a bit surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.15,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,At what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:57.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause, well, you seemed to really be into it, Rio-sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:02.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,If it were to get out that we illegally distilled this{moonshine xD}, we \Nwouldn't get off with just a court-martial. {kore no mitsuzou barettara gunbou kaigi jya sumanai hanashi nano ni}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Violation of monopoly and tax laws, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,At worst, treason, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:15.13,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sidejob that we took over from our predecessors{sempai-tachi}, but Rio's never once opposed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,I found it somewhat unexpected, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.43,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was shocked at the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:33.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,When I learned that the calvados my mother so loved was made at the bastion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:38.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Then the reason why you ended up assigned to this troop...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:42.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,might have been perhaps because your mother guided you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!  I'll be back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready!  Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:18.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,It looks wonderful, Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.20,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Today's their first visit to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:32.20,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,The priest will also be present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,So for today at least—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:34.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cause trouble for Sis, Mishio! {onee-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about just doing up your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,No!  {\i1}I won't{\i0}! {absolutely not}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.74,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Why not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.40,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,You always tell me to be good and just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:55.82,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't do things like that, Mishio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:00.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:08.55,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,10 yen and 25 sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.08,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, missy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:16.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!  I got a little too caught up—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.05,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,Man.  Watch yourself. {be more careful}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Alt,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They're the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:24.55,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they've managed to get wind of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? {i'm SO TERRIBLE with these names ;_; sorry for all my guys and dudes and whatnot x.x}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.15,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, Naomi-san—!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:36.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:40.87,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've had enough money in my wallet to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:43.73,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,If I asked for it now, I could actually end up buying it, couldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what would you do if someone came by and snatched it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone who said they wanted it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was just a "what-if" situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:00.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, let me see, if that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:05.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Right!  I would tell them that dolphins are very scary animals that will even eat humans!  And make them give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:08.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and that dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:16.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set it aside for you until you say that you don't want it anymore, so don't worry about it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:21.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Then I suppose I'll pick up everyone's presents first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:33.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Poppa and Momma, Grandpa and Grandma, Grandpa and Grandma from Waren, Great-Grandma, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,one for Grandma Nanae next door, too! {nanae isn't actually related to her, just an old lady that she's close to and so uses a baa-chan for}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:42.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... they're selling all sorts of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.24,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:45.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Shopkeep,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Mishio-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Are you shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Shopkeep,0000,0000,0000,,She says she's looking for a box or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:56.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,"A box"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.18,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen anything like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.31,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I help you look for it? {literal: f you're looking for it, shall i help you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.62,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:16.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!  Well you see, I came here to buy some presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:20.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to find some wonderful things to send back to my family in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not in a hurry, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.82,SoRaNoWoTo-Alt,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:35.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened with Mishio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:42.57,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:46.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,This one's cute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:57.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kanata-san... have you seen Mishio-san by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:58.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,"A box"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  She said it was something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:13.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,When her mother passed away, all of their belongings fell into other people's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:19.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,That box is supposedly a memento of her mother that was also taken at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Every time there's a market that comes in,\N she thinks that maybe, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I've... said something I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:33.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I received my wages for the first time yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And so I told her that I was here to buy presents to send home to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.29,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,That's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:44.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I — actually, we have every intention of being Mishio's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:53.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,If Mishio is still envious of others, that's entirely because I haven't reached that goal yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.48,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:10.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more important, me or your treasure box?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,This one right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:38.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:45.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mustache,0000,0000,0000,,And these are the famous Treize firecrackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:47.06,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mustache,0000,0000,0000,,They sound great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:47.78,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mustache,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:54.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Sis... {onee-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-oneechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.87,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:16:59.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{how did she get up there so fast?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,T-The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:17.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry it wasn't Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.27,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:28.59,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mustache,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:29.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Job well done! {how do you fire guns and make sparks and all but not shoot anything?! is that even possible? i'm sure it is but...whaaa x.x}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:34.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0025,,All right then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:35.97,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0025,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.53,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0025,,O-Oh!  What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:47.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0025,,It couldn't be that... that's {\i1}your{\i0} car, is it, Naomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0025,,No way, it was you guys who—!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:56.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,We're so sorry!  Ah!  Here's 150 yen as compensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.95,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that safe, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,I've already gotten my payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,N-Naomi-san, that box! {she doesn't say box, she just says that}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:19.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,These ideograms mean "beautiful stalk of rice."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:26.50,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,If you carve these into her seal, I'm sure she will have a plentiful, thriving life, like a full field of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:27.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:32.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, it's good that you received such a nice name{signature/maybe we should just put name. i think it's this word http://jisho.org/words?jap=%E8%8A%B1%E6%8A%BC&eng=&dict=edict}, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find Mishio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:50.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,I had planned to devote myself to becoming family for that girl, but I'm still an amateur.{or whatever word you feel fits best: http://jisho.org/words?jap=mijyuku&eng=&dict=edict. ano ko no kazoku ni nareru you ni to kokoro wo kudaitekita tsumori desu ga mada mada mijyuku desu}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.14,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how wonderful!  You've found it, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:12.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure it.  Treasure those irreplaceable{it's supposed to sound really good/nice. so if this sounds bad/sarcastic, maybe change it to indispensable, invaluable, etc.} memories of your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:13.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:18.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,This... I want Yumina to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,{awww wahhhhhh}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:32.40,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio is a child who lost her parents and so was taken in by the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:38.76,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,First, her father departed for the front and did not return...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.15,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:45.99,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio's family lived on the eastern border, in a town named Vingt. {i have no idea how to spell that. it's probably a number on that map? i think it may be 20 - that one begins with a v and ends in gt. people wrote numbers over the names though so i can't see it -_-}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:52.03,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they lived in the town attacked by that invisible death reaper. {mienai shinigami}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:59.05,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,And when the two of them came to Seize, her mother was already showing symptoms of illness, so soon after...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:04.29,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Mama said to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:08.32,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,that she was sorry she couldn't do my hair for me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:15.98,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,And also... and also, that I should have the person who would care for me the most from now on to do it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:20.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Will you do it for me, Yumina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:28.33,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,People live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:34.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we are parted from our loved ones and so go through\N times so tough that we think we'll pass on,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,despite that, we will still live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,We're still able to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:44.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,That strength is a very sad, very precious thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:50.52,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.89,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.74,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Right!  I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:14.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,You're tired, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:21.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  If I could've, I even wanted to skip on washing my hair, but... well, things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:26.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, sempai, please let me dry your hair for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.89,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to touch it! {LOL WHAT? Innuendo much? ~Sumi}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:36.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you didn't end up buying the dolphin, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought that was going to be your reward to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:45.88,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-sempai, do you believe in fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:47.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:53.24,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that... something happened today which made me think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:56.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And that was more than enough for my reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in it, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:04.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I hate things that are already decided ahead of time,\N or given to you from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:09.18,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Only... well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:15.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,It might be possible that the pure coincidences that someone creates may cause ripples
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:19.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,that could in turn cause big changes in other people's lives. {sou da na. dareka no umidashita guuzen ga meguri megutte tanin no jinsei wo ookiku kaeru koto ha aru no kamoshirenai}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:30.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,If you can call that fate, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:39.20,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:49.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you also had a wonderful day today, too, sempai.
